    "answer_id" : 22289526,
    "question_id" : 4830253,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you are working with a Mac... the keytool is part of the Java SDK and can be found in the following location /System/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/[VERSION].jdk/Contents/Home/bin/keytool</p>\n"
  }, {
