    "answer_id" : 22533886,
    "question_id" : 4830253,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you have java installed of course keytool is in there. What you need to do is to add it on your PATH variable.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 468563,
      "reputation" : 128,
