    "question_id" : 4830253,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For Android Studio users</p>\n<p>If you have Android installed in windows, you will also find it here:</p>\n<p><strong>C:\\Program Files\\Android\\Android Studio\\jre\\bin</strong></p>\n<p>Add this path in Enviourment variables and save it\nAfter then you can use keytool on your terminal/command prompt</p>\n"
  } ],
